description:
This is a 13 minute workout called 'Bedtime Yoga Stretch to Release Tension and Stress' from the channel Yoga With Bird.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Sleep Prep and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Do this bedtime yoga stretch to release tension and stress from the body and mind.
